{"tid":1593364,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[英超兩隊鏝]曼聯最新財政報告：解僱摩連奴花費1960萬鎊, 仍盈利5000萬","createTime":"2019-09-25T04:47:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T05:37:02.000Z","uid":103207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e76bcddb74fb1723966bbae867a5054d6ab39cc2","tid":1593364,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:47:58.000Z","msg":"曼聯官方財報：解僱摩連奴花費1960萬鎊<br />\n<br />\n  在這份財報中，<span style=\"color: red;\">前曼聯教練摩連奴的解約金獲得了體現，財報中稱：「今年的一項特別款項為1960萬英鎊，這項支出與前教練和部分教練組成員的離職補償有關</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n窮到只剩錢！曼聯最新財政報告：盈利5000萬<br />\n<br />\n  曼聯球會官方發佈了年度財報，這份財報中顯示，<span style=\"color: red;\">曼聯在2019財年中收入6.271億英鎊，相較於上個財年增長6%。球會營業利潤為5000萬英鎊。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebdb2977b7cc52f3d5eb46a1814b434f5e920d3a","tid":1593364,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:48:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"e591fb61745beb141e12a1a280f6708779d5b806","tid":1593364,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:25:05.000Z","msg":"Man U<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92002e3e9fe103f51416b5dfb9c604d85d733973","tid":1593364,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:28:25.000Z","msg":"Woodward賺錢好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c65aa750b7e48afba92e7fddb8473924daf03f6","tid":1593364,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92002e3e9fe103f51416b5dfb9c604d85d733973","tid":1593364,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:28:25.000Z","msg":"Woodward賺錢好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:31:42.000Z","msg":"所以係唔會炒佢"},{"pid":"f0d0110895c80af85a5a9ae2c4ff63adebb97047","tid":1593364,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:37:02.000Z","msg":"C朗筆錢屈能到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}